---
layout: base.njk
title: Share Feedback | Daily Pick
description: Tell the Daily Pick team what you love, what needs work, and what tools you want us to build next.
keywords: feedback, feature request, support, daily pick
permalink: /feedback/index.html
headExtra: |
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/assets/css/feedback.css">
---

<div class="feedback-page">
  <section class="feedback-hero">
    <div class="feedback-hero__heading">
      <p class="section-eyebrow">Feedback</p>
      <h1>
        <span>Help us level up</span>
        <span>Daily Pick</span>
      </h1>
    </div>
    <p>
      Share your ideas, requests, and success stories so we can keep improving the games and tools your team loves.
      Every note helps us prioritize the next round of updates.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="feedback-layout">
    <div class="feedback-form-card">
      <h2>Share your thoughts</h2>
      <p class="feedback-note">
        Tell us what&apos;s working well, what feels clunky, or what you wish existed. We read every response.
      </p>

      <form
        class="feedback-form"
        action="https://formsubmit.co/hello@dailypick.dev"
        method="POST"
        data-feedback-form
        data-endpoint="https://formsubmit.co/ajax/hello@dailypick.dev"
      >
        <input type="hidden" name="_subject" value="New Daily Pick feedback">
        <input type="hidden" name="_template" value="table">
        <input type="hidden" name="_next" value="{{ metadata.url }}/feedback/thank-you/">
        <input type="hidden" name="_captcha" value="false">

        <div class="feedback-field">
          <label for="feedback-name">Name <span>(optional)</span></label>
          <input id="feedback-name" name="name" type="text" autocomplete="name" placeholder="Pat from Team Rocket">
        </div>

        <div class="feedback-field">
          <label for="feedback-email">Email <span>(optional, only if you want a reply)</span></label>
          <input
            id="feedback-email"
            name="email"
            type="email"
            inputmode="email"
            autocomplete="email"
            placeholder="you@email.com"
          >
        </div>

        <div class="feedback-field">
          <label for="feedback-role">How do you use Daily Pick?</label>
          <select id="feedback-role" name="usage" required>
            <option value="" disabled selected>Select the best match</option>
            <option value="standup-facilitator">Running daily stand-ups</option>
            <option value="agile-coach">Agile coach or scrum master</option>
            <option value="team-member">Team member / participant</option>
            <option value="educator">Educator or trainer</option>
            <option value="event-host">Event host or facilitator</option>
            <option value="just-curious">Just exploring for fun</option>
          </select>
        </div>

        <div class="feedback-field">
          <label for="feedback-message">What should we know?</label>
          <textarea
            id="feedback-message"
            name="message"
            required
            placeholder="Share your ideas, bugs, or feature requests..."
          ></textarea>
        </div>

        <div class="feedback-actions">
          <button class="btn btn--accent" type="submit">Send feedback</button>
          <p
            class="form-alert form-alert--success"
            data-feedback-success
            aria-hidden="true"
            role="status"
          ></p>
          <p
            class="form-alert form-alert--error"
            data-feedback-error
            aria-hidden="true"
            role="alert"
          ></p>
          <p class="feedback-note">
            We use your email only to follow up on your submission. No spam, promise.
          </p>
        </div>
      </form>

      <p class="feedback-powered">
        Securely powered by <a href="https://formsubmit.co/" rel="noopener" target="_blank">FormSubmit</a> â€“ no
        account required.
      </p>
    </div>

    <aside class="feedback-aside" aria-label="Ways you can help">
      <h2>Wondering what to share?</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Tell us which games your team uses most and why.</li>
        <li>Suggest new rituals, icebreakers, or productivity boosts.</li>
        <li>Report bugs or rough edges so we can smooth them out quickly.</li>
        <li>Let us know if you want integrations or export options.</li>
      </ul>
    </aside>
  </section>
</div>

<script src="/assets/js/feedback.js" defer></script>
